<h5 id="subject_774438">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=d02c2b8ebfdf44378e526f6c0f474323&amp;topic=77570.msg774438#msg774438" rel="nofollow">Re: 钢之守护神RPG（メタリックガーディアンRPG）-规则书</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_774438'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_774438'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
